). Anterior margin of prodorsum with short notched rounded projection medially. Dorsum mainly striated, prodorsum with smooth patch dorsocentrally; opisthosoma rugose medially, with diagonal striations laterally; dorsal body setae lanceolate and serrate, subequal in length. Band of transverse striae between prodorsum and opisthosoma.

